article.headline: Grant-Foster scores 29, Grand Canyon tops Stephen F. Austin 80-58
article.description: — Tyon Grant-Foster scored 29 points to help Grand Canyon defeat Stephen F. Austin 80-58 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Grant-Foster scores 29, Grand Canyon tops Stephen F. Austin 80-58

article.story: PHOENIX -- — Tyon Grant-Foster scored 29 points to help Grand Canyon defeat Stephen F. Austin 80-58 on Saturday night. Grant-Foster also had six rebounds and blocked four shots for the Antelopes (26-4, 16-3 Western Athletic Conference). Rayshon Harrison added 19 points, seven assists and five rebounds. The Lumberjacks (15-14, 8-10) were led by Latrell Jossell with 18 points and five assists. Frank Staine added 14 points and Nana Antwi-Boasiako scored 10. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
